Description: EasyNewsletter
        ==============
        
        A newsletter for Plone.
        
        Features
        ========
        
        - Plonish (uses Plone's Collections to collect content)
        
        - Subscribing / Unsubscribing
        
        - Variable templates to generate a newsletter
        
        Documentation
        =============
        
        For more documentation please visit: http://packages.python.org/EasyNewsletter/
        
        Changes
        =======
        
        1.0 beta 1 (2009-09-19)
        ---------------------
        
        * First version for Plone 3
